<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>DESCRIPTION<sp/>OF<sp/>CONTENT<sp/>OF<sp/>THE<sp/>PACKAGE</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>package<sp/>is<sp/>composed<sp/>of:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Four<sp/>nodes:<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>go_to_point.py</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>position_service.cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>state_machine.cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Three<sp/>custom<sp/>services:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Command.srv</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Position.srv</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>RandomPosition.srv</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>One<sp/>launch<sp/>file:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>sim.launch</highlight></codeline>
